<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The <link linkend="_struct_algo_initializer">AlgoInitializer</link> struct represents the parameters required to initialize the algorithm. </para>



<para>the idea is to create an easy to use all-in-one struct to init the algo with std::string name, std::string guid, int algoid, ExchangeSender&amp; ordsender, vector&lt;int&gt; channels, int cpu, CmeSecMaster &amp; sec </para>
</section>
